platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love Imprint’s approach to learning. Beautifully animated visuals accompany click-through summaries from best-selling books and professional courses. Take quizzes along the way and save insights for reference. With a large library and many topics to choose from, there is something for everyone.

On adore cette approche éducative. De magnifiques graphismes animés illustrent des résumés de best-sellers et de cours professionnels.
透過精美動畫特效呈現暢銷書與專業課程的點擊式摘要，帶來別開生面的學習方式。
